title: 1989–90 North West Counties Football League
text:
The 1989–90 North West Counties Football League season was the eighth in the history of the <a href="North%20West%20Counties%20Football%20League">North West Counties Football League</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in <a href="England">England</a>. Teams were divided into two divisions: Division One and Division Two.
